title: liquid or debris in USB port and my phone has no battery
content: i check my phone and notice it doesnt charge i see the "liquid or debris in USB port" messege and even tho my phone never got close to water today... i checked for debris. nothing. i put it in rice for 15 mins just incase but when i take it off it is at 1% i try to plug it in. no luck. my phone shuts down and doesnt charge. i tryed plugging and leaving it and it just shows 0% for more than 10 mins. it is now back in the rice i dont know how to fix this issue please help :/
